7\/prophet-treat-prisoners-well\/","url_meta":{"origin":5708,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Captives: The Prophet commands good treatment of prisoners","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu 'Aziz ibn 'Umayr reported: I was among the prisoners of war on the day of the battle of Badr. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI enjoin you to treat the captives well.\u201d I was among the Ansar after I accepted Islam. When lunch\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7681,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/prophet-well-mannered-guest\/","url_meta":{"origin":5708,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Guests: The Prophet is a well-mannered guest","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, visited a house among the Ansar and he ate a meal with them. When the Prophet intended to leave, he asked for a place in the house to pray. A mat was placed, water was sprinkled\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5708","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-j